3
00:01:51,960 --> 00:01:53,080
When did you get here?

4
00:01:57,960 --> 00:01:59,240
What kind of poison did you get?

5
00:01:59,240 --> 00:02:00,440
Why did you ask me to treat you?

6
00:02:01,320 --> 00:02:02,760
It's the Wangu Poison Needle.

7
00:02:04,640 --> 00:02:05,920
We'll do it ourselves.

8
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,640
I said we'd do it ourselves.

9
00:02:10,036 --> 00:02:11,520
Su Yin.

10
00:02:11,520 --> 00:02:12,240
We haven't seen each other in a few years.

11
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,880
How did you become so noisy?

12
00:02:17,080 --> 00:02:17,880
Give me your hand.

13
00:02:55,150 --> 00:02:56,080
What's wrong?

14
00:02:57,520 --> 00:02:58,760
I forgot to tell you

15
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,680
that it hurts.

16
00:03:09,025 --> 00:03:11,400
All your joints are pricked with needles.

17
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:15,420
Be prepared.

18
00:03:15,420 --> 00:03:18,480
The first rain in the mid-autumn is coming.

19
00:03:18,480 --> 00:03:19,280
At that time,

20
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:22,080
the poison will take full effect.

21
00:03:23,800 --> 00:03:25,640
It seems that the poisoner

22
00:03:27,040 --> 00:03:28,520
picked a great time.

23
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:29,600
Don't talk nonsense.

24
00:03:29,600 --> 00:03:30,560
Can you cure him or not?

25
00:03:32,560 --> 00:03:33,880
I can't.

26
00:03:33,880 --> 00:03:34,960
Let him wait to die.

27
00:03:36,825 --> 00:03:37,905
What?

28
00:03:40,560 --> 00:03:41,920
