29
00:03:46,980 --> 00:03:49,600
If you want to cure him,

30
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:52,620
you have to collect seven crimson dahlias.

31
00:03:52,620 --> 00:03:53,920
Crimson what?

32
00:03:55,560 --> 00:03:57,480
Crimson dahlia

33
00:03:57,480 --> 00:03:58,800
is the most precious herb.

34
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:02,880
It grows on Chifeng Cliff.

35
00:04:02,880 --> 00:04:05,320
It blooms only once every seven years,

36
00:04:05,320 --> 00:04:06,800
with only one flower at a time.

37
00:04:07,680 --> 00:04:09,480
It's very dangerous to collect it.

38
00:04:11,200 --> 00:04:12,400
And

39
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:14,660
even if you collect seven crimson dahlias,

40
00:04:14,660 --> 00:04:16,340
you will only be able to cure him

41
00:04:16,340 --> 00:04:19,400
on seven consecutive sunny days before spring.

42
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,840
If one raindrop falls,

43
00:04:23,760 --> 00:04:25,400
your work will be wasted.

44
00:04:26,480 --> 00:04:27,920
That's why I said I couldn't cure him.

45
00:04:47,070 --> 00:04:49,050
Is there really only one way?

46
00:04:49,050 --> 00:04:49,850
Of course.

47
00:04:52,070 --> 00:04:53,710
Give me some time.

48
00:04:53,710 --> 00:04:55,350
I'll find it.

49
00:04:55,350 --> 00:04:57,470
