83
00:06:45,710 --> 00:06:47,150
as long as you are willing to serve him.

84
00:06:47,870 --> 00:06:49,030
You've been

85
00:06:49,030 --> 00:06:50,830
serving your young master.

86
00:06:50,830 --> 00:06:53,230
Now, you have a chance to repay him.

87
00:06:55,270 --> 00:06:57,590
Would you like to serve him

88
00:06:57,590 --> 00:06:58,350
for the sake of your young master's life?

89
00:06:58,350 --> 00:06:59,390
I'd like to.

90
00:06:59,390 --> 00:07:01,950
My young master treats me well.

91
00:07:01,950 --> 00:07:05,390
I'm willing to do anything for him.

92
00:07:06,110 --> 00:07:07,590
Hey.

93
00:07:07,590 --> 00:07:08,390
By the way,

94
00:07:09,790 --> 00:07:12,470
