95
00:07:12,470 --> 00:07:13,950
You have to bear with him.

96
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:15,150
Don't offend him.

97
00:07:15,950 --> 00:07:16,950
Don't worry, Your Highness.

98
00:07:16,950 --> 00:07:18,790
