99
00:07:18,790 --> 00:07:20,150
I'm the best at serving people.

100
00:07:20,150 --> 00:07:22,390
I promise to serve him well

101
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:24,670
so he will cure my young master.

102
00:07:37,270 --> 00:07:39,230
I volunteered to serve the miracle doctor.

103
00:07:39,230 --> 00:07:41,350
I wasn't forced.

104
00:07:41,350 --> 00:07:42,070
Really?

105
00:07:42,070 --> 00:07:42,950
Really.

106
00:07:42,950 --> 00:07:44,870
Dr. Que appreciates my talents.

107
00:07:45,590 --> 00:07:47,350
Your talents?

108
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:50,790
I'm the best at serving people in the world.

109
00:07:51,870 --> 00:07:53,510
He's eccentric.

110
00:07:53,510 --> 00:07:54,510
