117
00:08:03,670 --> 00:08:04,830
Come on.

118
00:08:04,830 --> 00:08:07,950
Do you think Que Siming
is some kind of bad guy?

119
00:08:08,950 --> 00:08:11,270
He just lacked someone he liked

120
00:08:11,270 --> 00:08:12,750
to serve him.

121
00:08:13,830 --> 00:08:16,550
Although Jinbao is not intelligent,

122
00:08:17,710 --> 00:08:18,830
he looks good.

123
00:08:24,830 --> 00:08:28,790
Why did he suddenly agree to stay?

124
00:08:28,790 --> 00:08:31,310
