125
00:08:35,590 --> 00:08:38,430
There's no point in him staying.

126
00:08:38,430 --> 00:08:39,710
Without a cure,

127
00:08:39,710 --> 00:08:41,070
how can he cure me?

128
00:08:41,830 --> 00:08:43,990
You can't make a silk purse…

129
00:08:43,990 --> 00:08:46,350
You can't make a silk purse out of a cow's ear.

130
00:08:47,710 --> 00:08:48,910
Yeah.

131
00:08:48,910 --> 00:08:50,070
