134
00:08:53,310 --> 00:08:54,790
All right.

135
00:08:54,790 --> 00:08:56,750
I let Que Siming stay

136
00:08:56,750 --> 00:08:58,470
because I have a way to find dahlias.

137
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,150
You just have to trust me

138
00:09:01,150 --> 00:09:02,110
like you used to.

139
00:09:03,110 --> 00:09:05,670
But dahilas are hard to get.

140
00:09:05,670 --> 00:09:07,030
How can you get them for me?

141
00:09:08,430 --> 00:09:10,630
I have no money at all.

142
00:09:10,630 --> 00:09:12,190
I can't pay you.

143
00:09:12,910 --> 00:09:14,230
Do you want to talk about it?

144
00:09:15,430 --> 00:09:16,230
Okay.

145
00:09:17,070 --> 00:09:18,510
From now on,

146
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:20,830
you must call me Brother.

147
00:09:20,830 --> 00:09:22,390
And you must listen to me.

148
00:09:22,390 --> 00:09:24,390
If I tell you to go to the east,

149
00:09:24,390 --> 00:09:26,150
