150
00:09:26,150 --> 00:09:29,910
I'll find some pretty girls for you in Annan.

151
00:09:29,910 --> 00:09:31,630
You will marry them

152
00:09:31,630 --> 00:09:33,190
and settle down.

153
00:09:33,190 --> 00:09:35,270
Your children

154
00:09:35,270 --> 00:09:38,390
will be my servants.

155
00:09:38,390 --> 00:09:39,230
