159
00:10:11,710 --> 00:10:14,270
The priest of Zangke Temple
is my grandfather's best friend.

160
00:10:14,270 --> 00:10:15,350
You can go there.

161
00:10:15,350 --> 00:10:16,710
The people of the Imperial Court
won't go there.

162
00:10:16,710 --> 00:10:18,030
You can live in peace.

163
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:22,620
Your Highness.

164
00:10:26,450 --> 00:10:27,850
Thank you very much.

165
