265
00:17:49,230 --> 00:17:50,510
Su Yin,

266
00:17:50,510 --> 00:17:51,950
use your internal energy
to unclog the circulation of qi and blood

267
00:17:51,950 --> 00:17:54,430
throughout his joints every three days.

268
00:17:55,150 --> 00:17:58,350
