But you kept shouting his name.

290
00:19:08,450 --> 00:19:12,130
Maybe thinking about him
will keep you conscious.

291
00:19:13,975 --> 00:19:15,975
What's your relationship with him?

292
00:19:15,975 --> 00:19:16,935
You and him…

293
00:19:17,750 --> 00:19:18,310
Come on.

294
00:19:18,310 --> 00:19:19,390
Don't talk about it.

295
00:19:19,390 --> 00:19:21,150
Get out, get out. Get out.

296
00:19:21,150 --> 00:19:22,450
Get out.

297
00:19:24,150 --> 00:19:25,830
Su Yin, I swear

298
00:19:25,830 --> 00:19:27,750
that is the last time I think of him.

299
00:19:30,130 --> 00:19:31,250
He ruined my home,

300
00:19:32,610 --> 00:19:35,570
and he put me where I am now.

301
00:19:36,490 --> 00:19:38,330
The more I think of him,

302
00:19:38,330 --> 00:19:39,450
the more I hurt.

303
00:19:40,290 --> 00:19:41,375
The more I hurt,

304
00:19:42,400 --> 00:19:43,800
the more I hate him.

305
00:19:46,950 --> 00:19:47,750
But I promise

306
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:50,260
that's the last time I think of him.

307
00:19:51,140 --> 00:19:52,275
Trust me.

308
00:19:52,275 --> 00:19:53,460
He's not worth it.

309
00:19:56,140 --> 00:19:57,020
It's all right.

310
00:19:57,020 --> 00:19:59,060
You can think of him

311
00:19:59,060 --> 00:19:59,980
or hate him.

312
00:20:00,740 --> 00:20:01,580
You can do whatever you want

313
00:20:01,580 --> 00:20:02,380
as long as you're happy.

314
00:20:02,380 --> 00:20:03,500
I don't want to think of him.

315
00:20:10,375 --> 00:20:12,255
Then, do your best to hate him.

316
00:20:21,700 --> 00:20:23,450
I got it from my grandfather.

317
00:20:23,450 --> 00:20:26,025
It has been seven years since it was picked.

318
00:20:26,025 --> 00:20:27,265
But it's not rotten at all.

319
00:20:28,100 --> 00:20:29,220
What an amazing flower.

320
00:20:33,220 --> 00:20:35,020
Xiaobao, it's great.

321
00:20:40,076 --> 00:20:41,500
In addition to this one,

322
00:20:41,500 --> 00:20:42,940
my dad found one for me.

323
00:20:43,740 --> 00:20:45,688
There's one in the palace.

324
00:20:45,688 --> 00:20:48,625
And the Tang Sect has one.

325
00:20:48,625 --> 00:20:51,625
I'm sure we'll collect all seven soon.

326
00:20:53,420 --> 00:20:56,980
You're so nice to Jin Xiaobao.

327
00:20:56,980 --> 00:21:00,660
Does he have something on you?

328
00:21:00,660 --> 00:21:02,340
No one is like you.

329
00:21:05,060 --> 00:21:08,980
I thought we were the same.

330
00:21:09,980 --> 00:21:11,180
- I thought you and him…
- Yin.

331
00:21:13,300 --> 00:21:14,100
Yin.

332
00:21:14,900 --> 00:21:15,700
Yin.

333
00:21:18,260 --> 00:21:19,180
Your Royal Highness.

334
00:21:19,180 --> 00:21:20,340
It's not appropriate.

335
00:21:22,363 --> 00:21:24,740
Yin, I told you

336
00:21:24,740 --> 00:21:26,300
that you don't have to call me
Your Royal Highness

337
00:21:26,300 --> 00:21:27,980
if there are no other people around.

338
00:21:28,816 --> 00:21:31,365
It's not appropriate to say your name.

339
00:21:31,365 --> 00:21:32,791
I am the Crown Prince.

340
00:21:32,791 --> 00:21:34,305
I say it's appropriate.

341
00:21:34,305 --> 00:21:36,180
Just call me by my name.

342
00:21:36,980 --> 00:21:37,700
Call me by my name, Yin.

343
00:21:37,700 --> 00:21:39,340
Call me by my name.

344
00:21:39,340 --> 00:21:40,140
All right. Shaoyu.

345
00:21:41,380 --> 00:21:42,260
Shaoyu, you…

346
00:21:42,260 --> 00:21:43,100
Please let go of me.

347
00:21:45,020 --> 00:21:45,540
No.

348
00:21:45,540 --> 00:21:46,940
I want to hold you a little longer.

349
00:21:47,660 --> 00:21:48,620
Yin.

350
00:21:48,620 --> 00:21:51,000
We haven't seen each other in three years.

351
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:52,480
Don't you miss me?

352
00:21:54,300 --> 00:21:55,500
What are you doing here?

353
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:58,420
Because I miss you.

354
00:21:59,620 --> 00:22:00,420
Nonsense.

355
00:22:01,620 --> 00:22:03,540
How can you leave Linjing
without His Majesty's authorization?

356
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:05,220
Well,

357
00:22:05,220 --> 00:22:06,380
I'll send someone to escort you back.

358
00:22:06,380 --> 00:22:07,020
No.

359
00:22:12,660 --> 00:22:14,300
Have you seen our grandpa?

360
00:22:14,300 --> 00:22:16,180
I'm not here to see him.

361
00:22:16,180 --> 00:22:17,980
Why do I have to go see him?

362
00:22:24,940 --> 00:22:26,980
The mansion hasn't changed at all.

363
00:22:26,980 --> 00:22:28,370
It's the same as when we were kids.

364
00:22:31,380 --> 00:22:32,500
Yin,

365
00:22:32,500 --> 00:22:34,620
I want to stay in my old courtyard.

366
00:22:35,500 --> 00:22:37,220
Someone is living in that courtyard.

367
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:38,180
I'll arrange for someone

368
00:22:38,180 --> 00:22:40,100
to tidy up the Plum Courtyard for you.

369
00:22:40,100 --> 00:22:41,060
No.

370
00:22:41,060 --> 00:22:43,380
Who is it?
Who is living in my courtyard?

371
00:22:45,100 --> 00:22:46,660
I don't care who he is.

372
00:22:46,660 --> 00:22:49,550
Get him out of my courtyard right now.

373
00:23:15,550 --> 00:23:16,940
Zhaocai, Jinbao.

374
00:23:17,800 --> 00:23:18,748
Young Master.

375
00:23:18,748 --> 00:23:19,780
Do you feel cold?

376
00:23:20,500 --> 00:23:22,001
Or are you hungry?

377
00:23:22,001 --> 00:23:24,220
Young Master, are you thirsty?

378
00:23:27,540 --> 00:23:29,260
You should

379
00:23:29,260 --> 00:23:30,900
work for Su Yin in the future.

380
00:23:36,450 --> 00:23:37,420
Young Master.

381
00:23:38,290 --> 00:23:39,708
Young master, what's wrong?

382
00:23:39,708 --> 00:23:41,230
Are you uncomfortable?

383
00:23:41,230 --> 00:23:41,950
Don't worry.

384
00:23:41,950 --> 00:23:43,270
I'll go get His Highness.

385
00:23:43,270 --> 00:23:44,390
I'll go get Dr. Que.

386
00:23:44,390 --> 00:23:45,870
No, listen to me.

387
00:23:47,425 --> 00:23:48,465
Don't worry.

388
00:23:50,380 --> 00:23:52,540
Su Yin did everything to save me.

389
00:23:52,540 --> 00:23:54,100
Even if I die of pain,

390
00:23:54,100 --> 00:23:55,420
I won't give up.

391
00:23:56,700 --> 00:23:59,740
I think your kung fu is amazing,

392
00:23:59,740 --> 00:24:02,140
so you shouldn't work as my servants.

393
00:24:03,425 --> 00:24:05,400
You'd better work for Su Yin

394
00:24:05,400 --> 00:24:06,980
and make a name for yourselves.

395
00:24:06,980 --> 00:24:09,612
So you can marry a good wife.

396
00:24:11,220 --> 00:24:12,340
I don't want to get married.

397
00:24:12,340 --> 00:24:14,675
I don't want to have a family, either.

398
00:24:14,675 --> 00:24:17,075
I want to stay with you forever.

399
00:24:19,350 --> 00:24:20,150
Young Master.

400
00:24:21,125 --> 00:24:22,075
Young Master.

401
00:24:22,980 --> 00:24:24,220
Jinbao and I

402
00:24:24,220 --> 00:24:26,050
learned our kung fu from you.

403
00:24:27,260 --> 00:24:29,140
Jinbao and I agreed

404
00:24:29,140 --> 00:24:32,300
to follow you in life or death.

405
00:24:33,220 --> 00:24:36,260
Young Master,
take care of yourself.

406
00:24:36,260 --> 00:24:38,540
When you get better,
get a wife and have children.

407
00:24:38,540 --> 00:24:40,900
Jinbao and I will guard your home.

408
00:24:40,900 --> 00:24:42,580
We'll be together forever.

409
00:24:43,340 --> 00:24:44,140
Right?

410
00:24:45,580 --> 00:24:46,460
Stop crying.

411
00:24:52,660 --> 00:24:53,180
Who is it?

412
00:24:53,180 --> 00:24:54,540
Who is living in my courtyard?

413
00:24:54,540 --> 00:24:55,900
Get out of there.

414
00:24:58,940 --> 00:24:59,780
It's you.

415
00:25:01,100 --> 00:25:02,860
What are you doing here?

416
00:25:08,020 --> 00:25:09,820
Don't mess around.

417
00:25:09,820 --> 00:25:12,180
Do you know who he is, Yin?

418
00:25:12,180 --> 00:25:14,060
His entire family should have been executed.

419
00:25:15,180 --> 00:25:17,620
I'll kill him today.

420
00:25:18,900 --> 00:25:20,925
I'll cut him into pieces.

421
00:25:25,820 --> 00:25:27,300
Su Yin, let go of me.

422
00:25:27,300 --> 00:25:28,660
How can you do this to me for him?

423
00:25:28,660 --> 00:25:29,340
Shaoyu.

424
00:25:30,220 --> 00:25:32,500
Xiaobao is my best friend.

425
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:34,550
As soon as you saw him,
you drew your sword against him.

426
00:25:34,550 --> 00:25:36,020
I had to stop you.

427
00:25:42,300 --> 00:25:43,740
But he is a criminal.

428
00:25:44,700 --> 00:25:46,580
He should have been escorted to Linjing
to be beheaded.

429
00:25:48,740 --> 00:25:50,460
He was framed.

430
00:25:50,460 --> 00:25:51,860
I will rehabilitate him.

431
00:25:52,727 --> 00:25:53,527
Shaoyu,

432
00:25:54,540 --> 00:25:56,820
I don't know what you had with Xiaobao before.

433
00:25:57,940 --> 00:25:59,380
But you're in my mansion.

434
00:25:59,380 --> 00:26:00,620
You should follow my rules.

435
00:26:01,676 --> 00:26:03,220
Xiaobao is sick.

436
00:26:03,220 --> 00:26:04,500
If you do anything

437
00:26:04,500 --> 00:26:06,500
against him,

438
00:26:07,700 --> 00:26:09,380
I won't leave you alone.

439
00:26:30,060 --> 00:26:31,460
He's the Crown Prince?

440
00:26:31,460 --> 00:26:32,660
No wonder he went after Huai'en.

441
00:26:35,380 --> 00:26:36,860
My grandfather

442
00:26:36,860 --> 00:26:38,420
stayed in Annan all these years.

443
00:26:39,420 --> 00:26:40,980
Since the emperor ascended the throne,

444
00:26:40,980 --> 00:26:42,380
he has always been afraid of my grandfather.

445
00:26:43,180 --> 00:26:45,100
The Crown Prince has been influenced
by the Queen since childhood,

446
00:26:45,100 --> 00:26:46,180
so he is narrow-minded

447
00:26:46,180 --> 00:26:47,140
and vengeful.

448
00:26:48,100 --> 00:26:50,060
So, I have to consider his status.

449
00:26:51,420 --> 00:26:52,380
Please stay away

450
00:26:52,380 --> 00:26:53,900
from him

451
00:26:53,900 --> 00:26:54,820
for days.

452
00:26:55,940 --> 00:26:56,380
Okay.

453
00:26:56,380 --> 00:26:57,380
I understand.

454
00:26:59,860 --> 00:27:01,220
You don't have to worry about it.

455
00:27:01,220 --> 00:27:02,820
I'll send someone to follow him.

456
00:27:02,820 --> 00:27:04,260
He wouldn't dare hurt you

457
00:27:04,260 --> 00:27:06,460
or tell anyone about you.

458
00:27:06,460 --> 00:27:07,580
Just recuperate at ease.

459
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:13,500
In fact, I thought a lot

460
00:27:13,500 --> 00:27:15,060
when I saw him today.

461
00:27:15,780 --> 00:27:18,380
I thought about

462
00:27:18,380 --> 00:27:19,580
how willful

463
00:27:19,580 --> 00:27:20,620
and foolhardy I was.

464
00:27:21,540 --> 00:27:23,660
I caused a lot of trouble for a lot of people.

465
00:27:25,740 --> 00:27:26,580
In the future,

466
00:27:26,580 --> 00:27:28,100
except for my parents,

467
00:27:28,100 --> 00:27:28,740
you,

468
00:27:28,740 --> 00:27:30,460
Zhaocai, and Jinbao,

469
00:27:30,460 --> 00:27:32,060
I won't care

470
00:27:32,060 --> 00:27:33,940
about anyone else or anything.

471
00:27:33,940 --> 00:27:35,060
And

472
00:27:35,060 --> 00:27:37,460
it's getting colder.

473
00:27:37,460 --> 00:27:38,700
I won't go out.

474
00:27:40,260 --> 00:27:41,500
So I won't run into him.

475
00:27:41,500 --> 00:27:42,460
Don't worry.

476
00:27:45,060 --> 00:27:45,860
Su Yin.

477
00:27:50,940 --> 00:27:51,940
Get some rest.

478
00:27:51,940 --> 00:27:53,460
I'll deal with him.

479
00:27:53,460 --> 00:27:54,780
Be careful.

480
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:06,020
Su Yin,

481
00:28:06,020 --> 00:28:08,420
you said you had nothing to do with him.

482
00:28:08,420 --> 00:28:10,420
Then why do you stay with him?

483
00:28:10,420 --> 00:28:12,340
I don't stay with him.

484
00:28:12,340 --> 00:28:14,260
I stay in the wing.

485
00:28:14,260 --> 00:28:15,500
I want to stay with you.

486
00:28:16,980 --> 00:28:17,580
No.

487
00:28:17,580 --> 00:28:19,540
That room is too small.

488
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:21,300
Be good. Stay in another courtyard.

489
00:28:21,300 --> 00:28:22,780
Then, ask him to stay in the wing.

490
00:28:22,780 --> 00:28:24,580
We will stay here.

491
00:28:24,580 --> 00:28:26,020
Shaoyu.

492
00:28:26,020 --> 00:28:26,780
Don't do this.

493
00:28:26,780 --> 00:28:28,020
Don't do that.

494
00:28:28,020 --> 00:28:29,980
You must be up to something.

495
00:28:31,220 --> 00:28:32,980
If you don't stay with me,

496
00:28:32,980 --> 00:28:34,460
I'll go back to the capital

497
00:28:34,460 --> 00:28:35,260
and tell my father

498
00:28:35,260 --> 00:28:36,900
that you are harboring a criminal.

499
00:28:36,900 --> 00:28:37,940
Okay.

500
00:28:37,940 --> 00:28:39,100
Go tell Prince Shen

501
00:28:39,100 --> 00:28:40,060
and His Majesty.

502
00:28:40,060 --> 00:28:41,260
Ask His Majesty to behead me.

503
00:28:44,140 --> 00:28:45,940
I just want to stay with you.

504
00:28:52,860 --> 00:28:53,420
Come with me.

505
00:28:54,140 --> 00:28:55,420
Let's go stay in another courtyard.

506
00:28:57,420 --> 00:28:58,340
Wherever is okay.

507
00:28:59,060 --> 00:29:00,860
Anyway, I want to stay with you.

508
00:29:06,660 --> 00:29:08,700
Your Highness, I found it out.

509
00:29:08,700 --> 00:29:10,260
The Crown Prince
didn't sneak out of the palace.

510
00:29:10,260 --> 00:29:11,300
He volunteered to go to Huaizhou

511
00:29:11,300 --> 00:29:13,100
and help Prince Shen and Li Gongxiang
put down the rebellion.

512
00:29:13,820 --> 00:29:15,780
He came here
from Prince Shen's Mansion the other day.

513
00:29:15,780 --> 00:29:16,740
His intentions are not clear.

514
00:29:18,620 --> 00:29:20,060
Inform all the secret guards in the mansion

515
00:29:20,060 --> 00:29:21,300
to be on heightened alert.

516
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:23,060
Don't leak the news.

517
00:29:24,060 --> 00:29:24,860
Yes.

518
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,375
Young Master.

519
00:29:51,375 --> 00:29:52,675
Please sit down.

520
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:02,460
I thought you were a young lady.

521
00:30:02,460 --> 00:30:04,780
You're waited on hand and foot.

522
00:30:05,860 --> 00:30:08,060
If I were a criminal,

523
00:30:08,060 --> 00:30:09,580
I would have killed myself.

524
00:30:09,580 --> 00:30:11,860
I would be ashamed to eat here.

525
00:30:11,860 --> 00:30:12,850
Shaoyu.

526
00:30:12,850 --> 00:30:14,300
What?

527
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:15,460
You don't want me to talk, huh?

528
00:30:18,200 --> 00:30:19,460
If you want to eat, eat.

529
00:30:20,340 --> 00:30:21,540
If you don't, get out.

530
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:34,875
Here.

531
00:31:03,700 --> 00:31:04,660
Your Highness.

532
00:31:11,010 --> 00:31:13,738
My uncle stayed in Annan for many years.

533
00:31:13,738 --> 00:31:15,620
He has great power.

534
00:31:15,620 --> 00:31:17,820
One minute, he promised to cooperate with me.

535
00:31:17,820 --> 00:31:20,380
The next, he took away my bait.

536
00:31:20,380 --> 00:31:21,220
Mr. Li,

537
00:31:23,600 --> 00:31:26,060
what do you think of it?

538
00:31:26,060 --> 00:31:28,220
His Highness didn't care
about politics for years.

539
00:31:28,220 --> 00:31:31,500
Su Yin has been in charge
of Prince Li's Mansion.

540
00:31:31,500 --> 00:31:32,780
His relationship with Jin Xiaobao

541
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:34,340
is unusual.

542
00:31:35,825 --> 00:31:38,020
It's him again.

543
00:31:38,020 --> 00:31:40,380
What's so special about him?

544
00:31:40,380 --> 00:31:42,860
Why are they all attracted to him?

545
00:31:42,860 --> 00:31:44,780
It doesn't matter what is special about him.

546
00:31:44,780 --> 00:31:47,980
It matters that we can use him.

547
00:31:49,060 --> 00:31:49,620
By the way,

548
00:31:50,540 --> 00:31:51,700
the second prince

549
00:31:51,700 --> 00:31:53,660
has sent Huai'en to Annan.

550
00:31:57,860 --> 00:32:01,420
I think he's here for Jin's possessions.

551
00:32:01,420 --> 00:32:05,500
We can take advantage
of this unique opportunity.

552
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:06,660
What do you think of it?

553
00:32:15,180 --> 00:32:16,100
Your Highness,

554
00:32:16,100 --> 00:32:18,620
some of Jin's possessions have not been found.

555
00:32:18,620 --> 00:32:21,980
Zongzheng Yuzhan and the imperial patrols
are looking for them.

556
00:32:21,980 --> 00:32:24,180
I'm afraid the Jin family is targeted.

557
00:32:26,660 --> 00:32:27,780
The Tang Sect

558
00:32:27,780 --> 00:32:29,500
still don't admit they have it, huh?

559
00:32:29,500 --> 00:32:30,460
Yes.

560
00:32:30,460 --> 00:32:32,180
They insisted
that they didn't have crimson dahlia.

561
00:32:34,460 --> 00:32:35,580
Your Highness,

562
00:32:35,580 --> 00:32:37,475
you have to take the initiative.

563
00:32:37,475 --> 00:32:39,395
Otherwise, Prince Shen and Li Gongxiang…

564
00:33:00,500 --> 00:33:01,260
Xiaobao.

565
00:33:02,660 --> 00:33:03,980
Xiaobao.

566
00:33:03,980 --> 00:33:05,575
Young Master.

567
00:33:05,575 --> 00:33:06,825
Come on.

568
00:33:08,100 --> 00:33:09,380
- Young Master.
- Xiaobao.

569
00:33:09,380 --> 00:33:10,580
Xiaobao, hand in there.

570
00:33:11,580 --> 00:33:12,420
Come on. Give me your hand.

571
00:33:12,420 --> 00:33:13,300
Young Master.

572
00:33:39,800 --> 00:33:40,680
Come on, Jinbao.

573
00:33:42,300 --> 00:33:43,550
Xiaobao.

574
00:34:55,860 --> 00:34:58,140
You're going to get my parents back?

575
00:34:59,075 --> 00:35:01,140
Zhaocai and Jinbao have already gone.

576
00:35:01,140 --> 00:35:01,950
But…

577
00:35:01,950 --> 00:35:04,060
Look where I am now.

578
00:35:04,060 --> 00:35:04,780
It's okay.

579
00:35:04,780 --> 00:35:08,040
I told them to tell your parents
you had a cold.

580
00:35:08,040 --> 00:35:09,640
The New Year is coming.

581
00:35:09,640 --> 00:35:11,280
If we don't get them back,

582
00:35:11,280 --> 00:35:12,660
they will be suspicious.

583
00:35:14,340 --> 00:35:15,260
All right, then.

584
00:35:19,220 --> 00:35:21,900
Tell someone to take down these curtains.

585
00:35:24,400 --> 00:35:26,100
All right.

586
00:35:30,917 --> 00:35:33,413
[Zangke Temple]

587
00:35:38,500 --> 00:35:39,660
Take care.

588
00:35:52,025 --> 00:35:53,025
Dear.

589
00:36:20,125 --> 00:36:21,125
Go.

590
00:36:24,625 --> 00:36:25,575
Go.

591
00:36:50,220 --> 00:36:51,740
How could they be gone?

592
00:36:52,980 --> 00:36:54,380
They had already been picked up

593
00:36:54,380 --> 00:36:56,180
by the time we got there.

594
00:36:56,180 --> 00:36:57,660
And there was no sign of a fight.

595
00:36:59,220 --> 00:37:01,620
Could it be the people of the Imperial Court?

596
00:37:01,620 --> 00:37:04,180
Will they kill them?

597
00:37:05,325 --> 00:37:06,260
No, they won't.

598
00:37:07,425 --> 00:37:08,950
People of the Imperial Court

599
00:37:08,950 --> 00:37:10,590
dare not kill them at Zangke Temple.

600
00:37:12,260 --> 00:37:14,660
Then, it must be Zongzheng Huai'en.

601
00:37:17,140 --> 00:37:18,500
What?

602
00:37:18,500 --> 00:37:19,580
How dare he do it again?

603
00:37:19,580 --> 00:37:20,420
What does he want?

604
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:22,580
I'll kill him.

605
00:37:23,460 --> 00:37:26,580
Think about it before you say it.

606
00:37:28,540 --> 00:37:29,500
Su Qi,

607
00:37:29,500 --> 00:37:30,940
gather your men

608
00:37:30,940 --> 00:37:32,300
and investigate it secretly.

609
00:37:32,300 --> 00:37:33,620
Zhaocai, Jinbao,

610
00:37:33,620 --> 00:37:37,380
tell everyone
not to mention it in front of Xiaobao.

611
00:37:38,540 --> 00:37:39,460
Let's have our stories straight.

612
00:37:39,460 --> 00:37:41,060
Tell them that Mr. and Mrs. Jin

613
00:37:41,060 --> 00:37:42,820
lit an eternal fire for Xiaobao at the temple.

614
00:37:42,820 --> 00:37:44,260
They need to stay there

615
00:37:44,260 --> 00:37:45,950
for a few more days.

616
00:37:45,950 --> 00:37:46,860
Yes.

617
00:38:04,037 --> 00:38:05,353
Dad.

618
00:38:05,353 --> 00:38:06,353
Mom.

619
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,540
Dad.

620
00:38:14,540 --> 00:38:15,336
Mom.

621
00:38:17,060 --> 00:38:18,300
Dad.

622
00:38:18,300 --> 00:38:19,109
Mom.

623
00:38:30,140 --> 00:38:32,740
I have prepared a mansion for you in Qianzhong.

624
00:38:34,380 --> 00:38:35,580
And you will have 30 servants

625
00:38:36,900 --> 00:38:38,140
and ten thousand taels of gold.

626
00:38:39,980 --> 00:38:41,020
I think that's enough for you.

627
00:38:42,580 --> 00:38:43,620
After the New Year,

628
00:38:44,540 --> 00:38:46,260
you get out of here.

629
00:38:49,300 --> 00:38:50,300
Where is Su Yin?

630
00:38:56,460 --> 00:38:57,820
Don't you know it?

631
00:38:58,700 --> 00:39:00,740
Your parents

632
00:39:00,740 --> 00:39:02,775
were taken away.

633
00:39:02,775 --> 00:39:05,415
Yin went to look for them.

634
00:39:09,820 --> 00:39:10,620
What?

635
00:39:12,140 --> 00:39:13,875
I guess

636
00:39:13,875 --> 00:39:16,395
my uncle's people took them.

637
00:39:19,075 --> 00:39:21,755
After all, you are criminals.

638
00:39:23,550 --> 00:39:27,350
You are guilty of a capital crime.

639
00:39:35,740 --> 00:39:37,260
Originally,

640
00:39:37,260 --> 00:39:39,340
I came to spend the New Year with Yin.

641
00:39:43,225 --> 00:39:45,140
But you ruined it.

642
00:39:45,140 --> 00:39:46,940
You're annoying.

643
00:39:49,140 --> 00:39:50,300
I've never

644
00:39:50,300 --> 00:39:51,340
seen someone

645
00:39:52,380 --> 00:39:55,100
as useless as you in my whole life.

646
00:39:55,100 --> 00:39:58,180
And you are mooching off of Yin.

647
00:39:58,180 --> 00:39:59,100
If I weren't afraid that he would be angry,

648
00:39:59,100 --> 00:40:00,620
I would have killed you.

649
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:02,020
It's not true.

650
00:40:02,020 --> 00:40:03,180
It's not true.

651
00:40:18,580 --> 00:40:19,380
Dad.

652
00:40:20,300 --> 00:40:21,580
You…

653
00:40:21,580 --> 00:40:22,460
What's wrong with you?

654
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:24,220
Dad.

655
00:40:27,700 --> 00:40:28,540
Xiaobao.

656
00:40:28,540 --> 00:40:29,980
Su Yin.

657
00:40:29,980 --> 00:40:30,780
It's not me.

658
00:40:32,060 --> 00:40:32,580
Xiaobao.

659
00:40:33,820 --> 00:40:36,180
Zhaocai, Jinbao, take him into the room.

660
00:40:36,180 --> 00:40:36,700
Come on.

661
00:40:38,740 --> 00:40:39,540
Young Master.

662
00:40:49,300 --> 00:40:51,407
I don't want to see you again.

663
00:40:56,580 --> 00:40:57,380
Get out of here.

664
00:40:58,500 --> 00:40:59,300
Get out of here.

665
00:41:03,340 --> 00:41:04,260
Su Yin.

666
00:41:04,260 --> 00:41:06,975
How could you do this to me for a pariah?

667
00:41:06,975 --> 00:41:09,180
You'll regret it.

668
00:41:09,180 --> 00:41:11,900
I am the future emperor.

669
00:41:11,900 --> 00:41:13,620
How could you do this to me?

670
00:41:18,740 --> 00:41:19,540
Go.

671
00:41:28,900 --> 00:41:31,925
[Prince Li's Mansion]

672
00:41:33,740 --> 00:41:34,780
Grandpa.

673
00:41:34,780 --> 00:41:36,260
The Jin family is not guilty
of a capital crime.

674
00:41:36,260 --> 00:41:37,300
The Imperial Court just wanted

675
00:41:37,300 --> 00:41:38,980
to use them to lure out the people behind them.

676
00:41:41,060 --> 00:41:42,580
Now that you know,

677
00:41:42,580 --> 00:41:45,620
why did you stop the Imperial Court
from arresting them?

678
00:41:45,620 --> 00:41:47,540
Mr. Jin saved my father.

679
00:41:47,540 --> 00:41:50,180
Xiaobao and I are best friends.

680
00:41:50,180 --> 00:41:51,380
Both emotionally and rationally,

681
00:41:51,380 --> 00:41:53,020
I shouldn't leave him alone.

682
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:57,340
I just want to do my best
to protect their lives.

683
00:41:58,900 --> 00:42:01,980
I will do my best
to protect the Imperial Court.

684
00:42:03,020 --> 00:42:05,140
No one is stopping you from repaying them.

685
00:42:05,140 --> 00:42:07,700
I've given the crimson dahlia to you.

686
00:42:08,925 --> 00:42:10,775
I am doing my best

687
00:42:10,775 --> 00:42:13,260
to keep the Imperial Court off you.

688
00:42:14,100 --> 00:42:15,060
What?

689
00:42:15,860 --> 00:42:18,060
Do you think that your mansion

690
00:42:18,060 --> 00:42:20,820
is an impregnable fortress?

691
00:42:25,300 --> 00:42:28,300
Prince Shen and Li Gongxiang
have arrived in Annan.

692
00:42:31,180 --> 00:42:31,980
What?

693
00:42:33,740 --> 00:42:37,020
I'm old.

694
00:42:37,020 --> 00:42:39,420
Even if the emperor is afraid of me,

695
00:42:39,420 --> 00:42:40,860
there must be an end to it.

696
00:42:41,940 --> 00:42:43,660
You are loyal to your friends.

697
00:42:43,660 --> 00:42:45,340
I won't get in the way.

698
00:42:45,340 --> 00:42:47,500
But you can't just be loyal to your friends.

699
00:42:48,450 --> 00:42:51,340
You should do your job.

700
00:42:53,025 --> 00:42:54,950
Go meet Prince Shen

701
00:42:54,950 --> 00:42:56,500
and see what he says.

702
00:42:58,140 --> 00:43:01,180
You have done enough for the Jin family.

703
00:43:01,180 --> 00:43:02,940
I think the young master of the Jin family

704
00:43:02,940 --> 00:43:05,740
will understand.

705
00:43:05,740 --> 00:43:06,780
If he doesn't understand,

706
00:43:06,780 --> 00:43:10,020
I will speak to him in person.

707
00:43:10,020 --> 00:43:10,860
No, Grandpa.

708
00:43:14,340 --> 00:43:15,660
I know what to do.

709
00:43:26,500 --> 00:43:28,766
Well, Young Master, are you hungry?

710
00:43:28,766 --> 00:43:29,860
I'll get you something to eat.

711
00:43:32,300 --> 00:43:33,940
- Zhaocai.
- Yeah.

712
00:43:33,940 --> 00:43:37,500
Go see if there's any news from my parents.

713
00:43:39,620 --> 00:43:40,380
Okay.
